item.title: Online Cyber Security Courses
item.description: Cybrary - Free courses in ethical hacking and advanced penetration testing. Advanced penetration testing courses are based on the book ‘Penetration Testing for Highly Secured Environments’. Coursera - 100% online learning from the world’s best universities and companies. Udemy - Choose from over 100,000 online video courses with new additions published every month. edX - Accelerate your future. Learn anytime, anywhere. MOOC.fi - The courses are offered by University of Helsinki’s Department of Computer Science.
